data.description: Welcome home to 1615 Creek Knoll, This Home features four great bedrooms and three full bathrooms. With a spacious square footage of 2,912, this traditional layout floor plan offers a formal living area and a formal dining room. Spacious living room, and a great walk-in pantry. Downstairs, you'll find a single bedroom that is great for visiting guests or a mother-in-law. Upstairs, you will be welcomed to a loft and a private craft room for all those hobbyists, along with bedrooms 2, 3, and the second full bathroom. The primary suite is definitely fit to suit all your needs when it comes to wanting more space. The primary bedroom features a quaint sitting space or office space, and the on-suite features double vanities, a separate shower, and an inviting soaking tub. The primary walk-in closet will definitely knock your socks off with over 150 square feet of space. Lastly, the backyard is welcomed by a backdrop of mature oak trees and a covered patio with plenty of space to entertain. All while being surrounded by a well-established neighborhood called Villages of WestCreek, where you can enjoy great amenities such as walking trails, two swimming pools, tennis courts, basketball courts, BBQ areas, pavilion rental available, a great clubhouse, and two great elementary schools within the neighborhood. At the edge of the neighborhood you will find horseback riding and a quaint petting zoo. Let's get you scheduled to see this home today.
